[h3 id=CityStreets 
	"City Streets
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"Starting with a hard level, City Streets requires a route before you start tasing it. So the route is:
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"The blue line is the path, the power point in the middle is the base, the big red dots are the enemies and the small orange dots are the power points.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"30 power points are located in this level, 20 of which you need to finish the 2nd mission.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	[img class=embed mw-100 src=https://i.postimg.cc/R0gS52cF/Action-Manroute.png 
	]img
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"First things first, the level spawns you with a silver car, which i immediately switch out to the motorcycle. The motorcycle is faster and can go through small passages, which is required.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"The first mission is to eliminate 8 of gangrenes forces, but what comes after the mission is more important; the 20 power points mission. 
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"After defeating the 8 enemies the game will give you the task to switch out your vehicle from the silver car to the motorcycle and then tell you to collect 20 power points. Luckily for me, i already switched to the faster vehicle and im both defeating the enemies and collecting power points at the same time.
	$LF
]div
[ul 
	[li 
		"Motorcycle: 1280 Speed, Address 11695A, every few frames a meteorite will be shot which deals ~130 damage.
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[div class=p 
	"Enemies in this level:
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"Every type of enemy has 500 HP
	$LF
]div
[ul 
	[li 
		"Roadster: Fat green vehicle, will shoot and sometimes try to ram you 
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[ul 
	[li 
		"Slammer: Red vehicle with yellow stripe in the middle, will ram you, aggressive
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[ul 
	[li 
		"Rammer: Fat yellow vehicle, will ram you, aggressive
		$LF
	]li
