[h4 id=MainEntranceSniperGuards1 
	"Main entrance (Sniper Guards 1)
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"The first sniper guards minigame. In this minigame we have to take out sniper guards with our longbow. On the 3rd kill i move from right to left so i can build up speed to hit the sniper guard that appears on the left 3 frames earlier.
	$LF
	"After collecting the 1st Code key i jump onto the railing and avoid going around the guard which saves a few frames.
