	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"You can climb up on the bridge and just jump across instead of having to turn the bridge. We need to turn the valves first and collect the gas mask though, so after collecting the gas mask i do the same skip but near the water. This skip can also be performed if you were to climb on
	$LF
	"the machine and try to jump over, which is what i do in a speedrun.
