	"Unfortunately, there is RNG at play, the same RNG all of the enemies in City Streets, Toxica and Speedster have. Once the boxes are destroyed, they will bounce up and down before exploding. This RNG is determined by when you destroy them.
	$LF
	"The power points inside of the boxes will always be the same.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"The first box i destroy and collect the power point from looks very awkward, but i could not find a faster way to do it. The rest of the boxes and power points look very good in optimization.
	$LF
]div
