[h3 id=BossDrX 
	"Boss - Dr.X
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"HP: 1000
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"The final boss. We need to use the energy gun to stun Dr.X and then attack the power pack located in the back of his exo-armor.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"Dr.X needs to be shot 8 times in each phase to reduce his HP to 200, where he becomes vulnerable. 
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"A few things to consider on this bossfight are:
	$LF
]div
[ul 
	[li 
		"Dr.X will always walk towards you and try to attack you with his electrified claw, knocking you down.
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[ul 
	[li 
		"You can slightly walk towards Dr.X while firing at him and once close enough, trigger his claw attack and turn around to avoid it.
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[ul 
	[li 
		"Dodging or getting hit by the claw will have Dr.X immediately start his next attack where he fires a green laser at you. In the 2nd phase (after a few hits in the back this attack changes to him shooting plasma balls).
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[ul 
	[li 
		"After being hit in the back, he will fly into the air and then come down after some time, which can be slightly manipulated by positioning yourself on the screen - saves a few frames each time.
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[div class=p 
	"The strategy is the same everytime:
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"-Shoot Dr.X 3 times before he gets too close to you, then trigger his claw attack by walking towards him for 1 frame
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"-Dr.X will start his next attack, enough time to get his HP down to 200 
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"-While he prepares his attack, Action Man needs to get as close to his back as possible so he can hit it on the first possible frame after getting Dr.X to 200 HP
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"In total: Dr.X needs to be hit in the back 8 times. It takes 525 frames to get him to 200 HP almost everytime. I was able to get him to 200 HP in just 523 frames on one phase, but this is extremely hard to do because Action Man needs to trigger
	$LF
	"Dr.X claw attack and turn around very fast while also shooting him in the side of the exo-armor. The hitbox needs to be manipulated somehow...
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"We get Dr.X to 200 HP for the last time and shoot him with the sniper, ending the game.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	[img class=embed mw-100 src=https://i.postimg.cc/0QT1hK59/e027f071f30ec31abd3100d1ab9abe77.png 
	]img
	$LF
]div
